name: DreamWeaver Core
description: Generates bedtime stories based on sleep duration and stress level. (Version 1)

name: DreamSound AI
description: Creates personalized soundscapes for relaxation and deep sleep. (Version 1)

name: DreamSketcher
description: Turns dream journal entries into calming illustrations. (Version 1)

name: NightCoach AI
description: Provides motivational messages and rituals before bedtime. (Version 1)

name: DreamPredictor
description: Analyzes habits to predict likelihood of vivid dreams. (Version 1)

name: DreamMix AI
description: Blends your favorite characters into custom dream-inspired stories. (Version 1)

name: DreamGuide AI
description: Suggests meditation exercises based on daily mood. (Version 1)

name: SleepSync AI
description: Syncs sleep data with wearable devices to adjust dream content. (Version 1)

name: DreamVisualizer
description: Transforms your sleep stats into colorful dream-style art. (Version 1)

name: DreamBuddy AI
description: A friendly chatbot that chats before bedtime to reduce stress. (Version 1)
